The paper deals with the secrecy transmission between clusters of mobile devices, which involves information theory (cs.IT) and network communication (cs.NI). The presence of a multi-antenna eavesdropper introduces the aspect of security (cs.CR). The proposed cooperative MIMO architecture involves multiple antennas and coordination among devices, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and systems and control (cs.SY).
